data.description: 4 bedroom/2 bath open floorplan with separate dining room, office, eat-in kitchen & upstairs bonus room. Large primary bedroom with separate closets, beautiful ensuite bathroom, tile shower and separate vanities. Gourmet kitchen with granite countertops & stainless appliances.  Crown molding & hardwood flooring in main living area with tile & carpet in the remainder of home. 2 car garage with storage. Back deck leads out to completely fenced backyard.  Call today for your very own private tour.
